%83%B95-%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E7%89%9B%E7%9C%8B%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4Pop%20Mart%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%A1%8D%E5%8D%87%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8D" target="_blank" uhash="39f1b78b805c775da0e4374177cd71dd"&gt;9992大行報告｜大摩調高泡泡瑪特目標價5%、最牛看幾多？預期今年Pop Mart大中華銷售額升近一倍&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;摩根士丹利將泡泡瑪特Pop Mart&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG09992/?mtc=20048" target="_blank" uhash="9d1d5dc1e6846f26ecd6281ae7ee02ab"&gt;（09992）&lt;/a&gt;基準目標價上調4.7%至382元，以反映今年純利預測升15%，令預測市盈率降到42倍；泡泡瑪特最牛情境目標價微升至483元，最熊情境目標價亦調高至181元；評級維持「增持」。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;大摩調高泡泡瑪特2025、2026及2027年純利4%至15%，因中國及海外市場收入預測提高，而且營運支出率下降，預期今年泡泡瑪特純利按年升257%至111億元（人民幣，下同），銷售額按年升167%至348億元；明年純利按年升31%至146億元，銷售額升30%至450億元。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32023698&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=119016032868b8a48e27c053_44555494"/><published>2025-09-03T19:52:32+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2ac495a099fd4990aaf1025422dfa6fe</id><title>低息貸款，有咩人借到！100萬24個月3厘七</title><updated>2025-09-03T20:16:53+08:00</updated><author><name>想想好嘛</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-03T20:16:53+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573844479"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573844479"&gt;堅定留，有冇師兄分享&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32023721&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=119016032868b8a48e27c053_44555494"/><published>2025-09-03T20:16:53+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9add75938352e32744b8119ee2badf3d</id><title>支持美股大升，瘋狂咁升，到時大插熊證利潤可觀</title><updated>2025-09-03T20:18:41+08:00</updated><author><name>煩惱自尋</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-03T20:18:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573844500"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573844500"&gt;大家點睇&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32023723&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=119016032868b8a48e27c053_44555494"/><published>2025-09-03T20:18:41+08:00</published></entry></feed>